{"word":"Harvest","slug":"harvest","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Harvest</b> Sabbath to be observed in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=21'>Exo 34:21</a><br/> Sabbath desecrated in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=22'>Neh 13:22</a><br/> Of wheat at Pentecost, in Palestine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=22'>Exo 34:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=17'>Lev 23:17</a><br/> Of wheat, before vintage<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=26&verse=5'>Lev 26:5</a><br/> Of barley, before wheat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=9&verse=32'>Exo 9:32</a><br/> Celebrated with joy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=9&verse=27'>Jdg 9:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=9&verse=3'>Isa 9:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=16&verse=10'>Isa 16:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=33'>Jer 48:33</a><br/> Promises of plentiful<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=8&verse=22'>Gen 8:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=5&verse=24'>Jer 5:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=2&verse=24'>Joe 2:24</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=24&verse=6'>Job 24:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=10&verse=5'>Pro 10:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=8&verse=20'>Jer 8:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=13'>Joe 3:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=37'>Mat 9:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=39'>Mat 13:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=2'>Luk 10:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=14&verse=15'>Rev 14:15</a><br/><a href='S:Pentecost, Called, Feast of Harvest'>Pentecost, Called, Feast of Harvest</a>; <a href='S:Tabernacles, Feast of'>Tabernacles, Feast of</a>; <a href='S:First Fruits'>First Fruits</a>; <a href='S:Reaping'>Reaping</a>; <a href='S:Gleaning'>Gleaning</a>"}]}